text: Farhan Khan (born 10 October 1990) is a Pakistani cricketer who plays for Lahore. He made his Twenty20 debut on 25 August 2016 for Lahore Blues in the 2016–17 National T20 Cup. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Pakistani cricketers Category:Lahore Blues cricketers Category:Lahore Eagles cricketers Category:Lahore Lions cricketers Category:State Bank of Pakistan cricketers Category:Cricketers from Lahore Category:Central Punjab cricketers
